snippet.title: Birding 101 - Gameplay Demo
snippet.description:
Play or download: https://anttihaavikko.itch.io/birding-101

In Birding 101, also known as How to Bird, you help a flock of birds accomplish the goals given to them by a mysterious totem. It's a simple 2D physics based puzzler with a handful of puzzles for you to solve.

The game was created from scratch in 48 hours for Global Game Jam 2018 / Finnigh Game Jam 2018.
